{
  "stem": "4187.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we were sure we would.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We always were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But anyway, this was a very small work camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it certainly wasn't an extermination camp, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was simply a little working camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, there, truly, the situation was far, far better, because there were little houses, actual houses, built by-- brick houses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had rooms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the rooms, yeah, they were bunks, but decent-- decent beds-- two beds, like kids have.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the situation there, from that point-- and we even had some heating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a little heater there that we-- because now, we're getting into winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was November.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we-- we worked in a munition factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my sister and I-- beg your pardon-- my sister and my mother were in one shift, and I was by myself in another.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were 12-hour shifts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I-- I saw nothing of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because we just didn't-- except on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We worked seven days, 12 hours-- beg your pardon-- six days, 12 hours, but not on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and I remember my birthday, November 30, we were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my work transport was walking up into the factory, and theirs was coming back from their shift.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my mother said, happy birthday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, so, the situation was really and truly acceptable there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "If that had been right through, would have been all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There is one thing that I-- I'd like to-- I'd like to tell the story of-- no, two things, in Duderstadt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One was that there was-- the German commander was living-- well, as I said, they were brick houses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And one of the rather attractive, nice, big, big house was his, the commander.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
